data.description: Welcome to your own private oasis nestled on over 9 wooded acres, where luxury meets nature in this custom home.You're greeted by an expansive open concept design, adorned w gleaming hardwood floor.The soaring cathedral ceilings elevate the ambiance, creating a sense of grandeur & openness.For the outdoor enthusiast, a 40' RV parking garage has been transformed into a single garage & apartment, offering versatile options such as a rental income opportunity or a private guest suite.Indulge in the ultimate relaxation within the primary suite, featuring a spacious walk-in closet to accommodate your wardrobe needs. The large pantry ensures ample storage space, while the stainless steel kitchen appliances elevate both style & functionality.Discover convenience in the second owner suite, boasting its own walk-in closet complete w a dedicated shoe shelf.But that's not all – this home is equipped w a unique bunker that presents endless possibilities as well as an encapulated crawlspace.
